  <original-body>Sometimes I use link_to to link an image. 

In rails 3 the name is always escaped:

    &quot;&lt;a #{href_attr}#{tag_options}&gt;#{ERB::Util.h(name || url)}&lt;/a&gt;&quot;.html_safe!

Can you add an option to link_to that matches the option on url_for so it accepts :escape like url_for does.</original-body>
